					<description><![CDATA[青葉が目にまぶしいこのごろ、皆様にはますますご健勝のこととお慶び申し上げます、 岡山の釣りガイジでございます。 前回の記事で釣ってきた、武庫川のチヌ、 https://ktslab.jp/?p=680 今回は調理です、ポ [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>青葉が目にまぶしいこのごろ、皆様にはますますご健勝のこととお慶び申し上げます、</p>



<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline">岡山の釣りガイジ</span></strong>でございます。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9754-1-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-717" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9754-1-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9754-1-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9754-1-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9754-1-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9754-1-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9754-1-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>前回の記事で釣ってきた、<span style="text-decoration: underline">武庫川のチヌ</span>、</p>



<p><a href="https://ktslab.jp/?p=680">https://ktslab.jp/?p=680</a></p>



<p>今回は調理です、<strong>ポワレ</strong>作っていきます。</p>



<p>っしゃ、やるぞ</p>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<p>まず、準備するもの、ポワレに必要なもの、其れは何と言っても<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline">BCAA</span></strong>、</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_1273-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-721" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_1273-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_1273-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_1273-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_1273-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_1273-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_1273-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline">BCAA</span></strong>とは、<span style="text-decoration: underline">分枝鎖アミノ酸</span>、要するにアミノ酸、<span style="text-decoration: underline">旨味成分</span>って事じゃ！（近からず遠からず）</p>



<p>筋トレ前、筋トレ中、筋トレ後、いつ摂取するかは人それぞれのタイミングだが、これを飲む事で筋肉が喜ぶ、筋肉嬉しいからデカくなる、という事。</p>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<p>さて、<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline">武庫川のチヌ</span></strong>を用意します。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="768" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9951.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-722" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9951.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9951-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9951-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p>そのほか使用する物はこちら</p>



<p>・トマト</p>



<p>・レモン</p>



<p>・バター</p>



<p>・ベビーリーフ</p>



<p>・BCAA</p>



<p>・塩胡椒</p>



<p>・オリーブオイル</p>



<p>・バジル</p>



<p>・ローリエパウダー</p>



<p>・粗挽きブラックペッパー</p>



<p>・料亭だし</p>



<p>下処理</p>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">1、トマト</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9954-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-723" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9954-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9954-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9954-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9954-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9954-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9954-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>トマトのへたを取り（取らなくても良いです）、コンカッセにしときます。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9960-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-724" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9960-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9960-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9960-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9960-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9960-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9960-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>（粗く角切、何でも良いです、ソースなので。）</p>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">2、レモン</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9961-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-725" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9961-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9961-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9961-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9961-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9961-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9961-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>軽く洗って、エマンセにします、薄切り、輪切りロンデルとも言って過言でない、種は取り除く \ﾀﾈﾅｼ/</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9962-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-726" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9962-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9962-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9962-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9962-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9962-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9962-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">3、BCAA</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9963-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-727" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9963-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9963-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9963-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9963-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9963-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9963-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>エクラゼにします、アッシェでもシズレ（スィズレ）でも良いですね、細かく砕きます。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9964-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-728" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9964-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9964-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9964-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9964-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9964-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9964-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>調理</p>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">1、焼きます。</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9966-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-729" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9966-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9966-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9966-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9966-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9966-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9966-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>　フライパンに、</p>



<p>オリーブオイル、トマト、レモン汁、バター、塩胡椒、BCAAを入れて炒める　　</p>



<p>あーあ。</p>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">2、忘れてたバターを入れる、雰囲気は美味そうですね。</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1024" height="682" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9968.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-730" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9968.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9968-300x200.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9968-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">3、出来上がったソースがこちら。</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9970-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-732" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9970-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9970-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9970-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9970-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9970-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9970-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>何だかとっても<strong>BCAA</strong>臭いので適当にスパイスで隠す。</p>



<p>（そんな臭くないと思ってたんだがな、、、BCAA）</p>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">4、万能調味料《料亭だし》岡山県倉敷市玉島中央町で作られている。</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9971-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-731" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9971-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9971-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9971-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9971-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9971-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9971-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p>整う、これさあれば何でも良い。</p>



<p>くっそ美味いソースの完成。</p>



<p>ソースができたらもうこっちのもんよ、</p>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">5、昨晩塩を振っておいたチヌ、水分を拭き取る</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9973-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-733" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9973-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9973-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9973-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9973-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9973-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9973-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">6、フライパンにオリーブオイルを塗布する。</h2>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">7、弱火でチヌを皮面から火入れしていく。</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9976-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-734" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9976-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9976-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9976-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9976-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9976-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9976-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">8、6分ほど焼いて、皮目が黄金色に、身の7 割に火が入ったところで裏返す。</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9977-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-735" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9977-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9977-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9977-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9977-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9977-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9977-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<h2 class="has-pale-cyan-blue-background-color has-background">9、身側に刹那の火入れをして完成、皿に盛り付けてディモールト、ボーノボーノ、とってもオッティモwww</h2>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="2560" height="1920" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9984-1-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-737" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9984-1-scaled-1.jpg 2560w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9984-1-scaled-1-300x225.jpg 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9984-1-scaled-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9984-1-scaled-1-768x576.jpg 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9984-1-scaled-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2022/05/img_9984-1-scaled-1-2048x1536.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></figure>



<p><strong>武庫川のチヌ</strong>、臭みとかはなく、めっちゃ美味い、<strong>武庫川のチヌ</strong>に感謝。ごちそうさまでした。</p>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<p>P.S.</p>



<p>最後まで読んでいただき、大変恐悦至極にございます。</p>



<p>この記事は何の参考にもなりませんが、BCAAはあらゆる調理を進化させる可能性を感じました。</p>



<p>微粒子程度でも皆様のお暇潰しになりましたら幸いに存じます。</p>



<p>チョベリグ。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
